s lijphart przeworski verba dataset award 2010 co pi of the detroit arab american study a sister survey to the detroit area study and senior advisor on the pew research center projects focusing on islam in america 2006 and global islam 2011 in 2005 jamal was named a carnegie scholar last modified thursday march 3 0726 1 23pm secondary links stanford home school of humanities and science contact login stanford university department of political science encina hall west suite 100 stanford california 94305 6044 phone 650 723 1806 fax 650 723 1808
